    <node id="Source15">
      <data key="d0">Source15</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Source15 is a data source containing clinical data from patients with ovarian high-grade serous carcinoma, as described in a proteogenomic study by McDermott et al.&lt;SEP&gt;Source15 is the source document providing the McDermott dataset and clinical table.</data>
