    <node id="Source16">
      <data key="d0">Source16</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Source16 is a data source providing a comprehensive dataset from the paper "A proteogenomic portrait of lung squamous cell carcinoma" by Satpathy et al, with detailed genomic and clinical information.&lt;SEP&gt;Source16 is the source document providing the Satpathy dataset and relevant sample table.&lt;SEP&gt;Source16 is the originating dataset or batch connected to the Satpathy table and various experimental fields.&lt;SEP&gt;Source16 is the data source from which the Satpathy table and associated fields are derived.&lt;SEP&gt;Source16 is the origin of the data, indicating a primary source for the Satpathy dataset.&lt;SEP&gt;Source16 is the origin of the Satpathy data table, which aggregates information on genetic mutations.&lt;SEP&gt;Source16 represents the origin or root of the data lineage associated with the omics features found in the Satpathy table.</data>
