      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">NMF Subtype is a variable in Satpathy.csv characterizing molecular subtypes in lung squamous cell carcinoma.&lt;SEP&gt;NMF Subtype captures sample membership based on non-negative matrix factorization clustering, including core subtype, score, and membership.&lt;SEP&gt;NMF Subtype denotes sample assignments based on non-negative matrix factorization clustering, such as "Classical" and "Basal inclusive."</data>
