    <node id="TCGA Pan-Can Immune Clustering">
      <data key="d0">TCGA Pan-Can Immune Clustering</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">TCGA Pan-Can Immune Clustering is a variable in Satpathy.csv describing immune characteristics across cancer types.&lt;SEP&gt;TCGA pan-can immune clustering is a data-derived classification of samples based on immune characteristics observed across various cancer types in TCGA.&lt;SEP&gt;TCGA Pan-Can Immune Clustering assigns colorectal cancer samples to immune-related categories such as Inflammatory or Lymphocyte depleted, based on pan-cancer RNA expression analysis.&lt;SEP&gt;TCGA Pan-Can Immune Clustering is a classification field in Satpathy based on TCGA pan-cancer immune cluster analysis.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-eb6086be52202affaf1f5509e67c615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d9939ff094898f5ac26a9ca6b9f24d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-940356a2b7fb1da402acf0a10ad5efd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4920e35caf575dd4b77bcddd5af16b21</data>
