      <data key="d2">StromalScore is a column in Vasaikar.csv quantifying the stromal content in cancer samples.&lt;SEP&gt;StromalScore quantifies the stromal content in a tissue sample based on gene expression.&lt;SEP&gt;StromalScore measures the activity level of stromal cells within a biological sample.</data>
