    <node id="Source12">
      <data key="d0">Source12</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Source12 is the identifier for a comprehensive dataset covering clinical, pathological, molecular, and immune parameters from a research study on lung adenocarcinoma.&lt;SEP&gt;Source12 is a data source that contains a comprehensive dataset from the study "Proteogenomic Characterization Reveals Therapeutic Vulnerabilities in Lung Adenocarcinoma" by Gillette, M.A., including patient and tumor metadata in a table named "Gillette.csv".&lt;SEP&gt;Source12 is referenced as the origin for sample and participant-related fields in Table Gillette.&lt;SEP&gt;Source12 is the source of the Gillette table, containing data fields related to participant experiments and measurements.&lt;SEP&gt;Source12 is the origin of the dataset containing a variety of tumor purity estimates, mutation information, and scores, processed in Table Gillette.&lt;SEP&gt;Source12 is identified as a data provider or data source contributing genetic mutation data for the Gillette dataset.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-0d91412336d61fb6f6f1476e85a124fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04b158694d39b0e83dca281e98be90f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b75a391c5f0b66b34d954f9a4cd3db18&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1528391f98541c081c44645142dbc460&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2c4bb739cfbcabcd7df2d04d21fe611&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56d9b31e2fe71c27aaee333b1280d702</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1772772445</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Proteogenomic Characterization Reveals Therapeutic Vulnerabilities in Lung Adenocarcinoma">
      <data key="d0">Proteogenomic Characterization Reveals Therapeutic Vulnerabilities in Lung Adenocarcinoma</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">Proteogenomic Characterization Reveals Therapeutic Vulnerabilities in Lung Adenocarcinoma is a research publication focusing on lung adenocarcinoma and uncovering therapeutic weaknesses using proteogenomic methods.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-0d91412336d61fb6f6f1476e85a124fa</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1772771112</data>
