      <data key="d0">Gillette, M.A.</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Gillette, M.A. is the author of the study titled "Proteogenomic Characterization Reveals Therapeutic Vulnerabilities in Lung Adenocarcinoma."&lt;SEP&gt;Gillette, M.A. is the author of the study "Proteogenomic Characterization Reveals Therapeutic Vulnerabilities in Lung Adenocarcinoma".</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-0d91412336d61fb6f6f1476e85a124fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04b158694d39b0e83dca281e98be90f2</data>
