    <node id="Lung Adenocarcinoma">
      <data key="d0">Lung Adenocarcinoma</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Lung adenocarcinoma is a type of lung cancer characterized by glandular differentiation and is the primary subject of the dataset and study.&lt;SEP&gt;Lung adenocarcinoma is a type of lung cancer analyzed in the study "Proteogenomic Characterization Reveals Therapeutic Vulnerabilities in Lung Adenocarcinoma".</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-0d91412336d61fb6f6f1476e85a124fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04b158694d39b0e83dca281e98be90f2</data>
