      <data key="d0">Clinical, Pathological, Molecular, and Immune Parameters Dataset</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">The Clinical, Pathological, Molecular, and Immune Parameters Dataset includes features such as lymph node status, staging information, tumor characteristics, receptor status, immune cell profiling, genomic alteration data, and sample identifiers.</data>
