      <data key="d2">ESTIMATE Stromal Score presents the stromal score calculation from the ESTIMATE methodology, with three distinct sample values.&lt;SEP&gt;ESTIMATE Stromal Score is a quantitative measure of stromal content in tumor samples, provided in the Huang.csv Table.&lt;SEP&gt;ESTIMATE stromal score is a quantitative score reflecting stromal cell activity in the tumor microenvironment.</data>
