      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">ESTIMATE Immune Score provides immune-related scoring across three sample sets using the ESTIMATE method.&lt;SEP&gt;ESTIMATE Immune Score quantifies immune infiltration in tumor samples, as recorded in the Huang.csv Table.&lt;SEP&gt;ESTIMATE immune score is a quantitative measure of immune cell activity within the tumor microenvironment.</data>
