      <data key="d2">Tumor Site Other records alternative anatomical locations for tumors in the Clark Table.&lt;SEP&gt;Tumor Site Other specifies combinations like 'Anterior and Posterior endometrium' for tumor locations in samples.&lt;SEP&gt;Tumor Site Other is a field in the Dou table from source11 that provides a textual description of the tumor location within the endometrium.</data>
