    <node id="Country Of Origin">
      <data key="d0">Country Of Origin</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Country Of Origin designates the country associated with each participant, sample, or data record, such as USA.&lt;SEP&gt;Country Of Origin indicates the participant's country of origin, for example, USA, in the Gillette table from source12.&lt;SEP&gt;Country Of Origin records the country where the individual originates from, as found in the Wang table of Source18.</data>
