      <data key="d0">Vascular Invasion</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Vascular Invasion describes whether cancer has invaded blood vessels in a sample.&lt;SEP&gt;Vascular Invasion is an indicator in the Vasaikar table reporting whether the tumor has invaded blood vessels.</data>
