    <node id="Lymphatic Invasion">
      <data key="d0">Lymphatic Invasion</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Lymphatic Invasion refers to the presence or absence of tumor invasion into lymphatic vessels.&lt;SEP&gt;Lymphatic Invasion describes whether lymphatic system invasion by tumor cells is present in the patient's record, as tracked in the Vasaikar table.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-61e42152f676545c1a94912cb5944a32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a16fce68df8a087312002be8f90c5ca4</data>
