      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Synchronous Tumors indicates whether a patient sample had more than one tumor present at the same time.&lt;SEP&gt;Synchronous Tumors indicates the simultaneous presence of multiple tumors in a patient, per the Vasaikar table.</data>
