      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Polyps History records whether a patient had a previous history of polyps.&lt;SEP&gt;Polyps History denotes whether there is a patient history of polyps, as indicated in the Vasaikar table.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-61e42152f676545c1a94912cb5944a32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a16fce68df8a087312002be8f90c5ca4</data>
