      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Tumor Status refers to the presence or absence of tumor at evaluation.&lt;SEP&gt;Tumor Status indicates if the patient is currently tumor-free or has an existing tumor according to the Vasaikar table.</data>
