    <node id="Samples">
      <data key="d0">Samples</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Samples contain generic numeric values possibly serving as initial or contextual measurements for the subsequent data sets.&lt;SEP&gt;Samples refer to the three individual data points being evaluated across all genomic and sequencing metrics in the input, serving as the basis for variant and mutation calculations.</data>
