    <node id="Pathologic Staging Regional Lymph Nodes Pn">
      <data key="d0">Pathologic Staging Regional Lymph Nodes Pn</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Pathologic Staging Regional Lymph Nodes Pn records the pathologic stage of regional lymph nodes, such as pN1 and pN2.&lt;SEP&gt;Pathologic Staging Regional Lymph Nodes Pn is a field in Table Cao, denoting nodal status according to pathological staging criteria (pN).</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-07e1af1bf39bca6afef0e83065e9d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b74bb3e12c83406f44983363ccf9e2f</data>
