      <data key="d0">Pathologic Staging Primary Tumor Pt</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Pathologic Staging Primary Tumor Pt records the pathologic stage of the primary tumor.&lt;SEP&gt;Pathologic Staging Primary Tumor Pt is a field in Table Cao, specifying the primary tumor's stage following pathological assessment (pT).</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-07e1af1bf39bca6afef0e83065e9d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b74bb3e12c83406f44983363ccf9e2f</data>
