      <data key="d0">Clinical Staging Distant Metastasis Cm</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Clinical Staging Distant Metastasis Cm records the clinical stage for distant metastasis.&lt;SEP&gt;Clinical Staging Distant Metastasis Cm is a field in Table Cao, referring to the clinical evaluation of distant metastasis (cM).</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-07e1af1bf39bca6afef0e83065e9d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b74bb3e12c83406f44983363ccf9e2f</data>
