    <node id="Tobacco Smoking History">
      <data key="d0">Tobacco Smoking History</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Tobacco Smoking History records the tobacco use history of participants.&lt;SEP&gt;Tobacco Smoking History is a field in Table Cao indicating past or current tobacco usage status of a patient.&lt;SEP&gt;Tobacco Smoking History is a data field describing patient history of tobacco use, including lifelong non-smoker and reformed smoker statuses, as found in Table Cao from source9.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-07e1af1bf39bca6afef0e83065e9d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f35709cd063c7f945768e5ca53cbe7fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b74bb3e12c83406f44983363ccf9e2f</data>
