    <node id="Nonsense_Mutation">
      <data key="d0">Nonsense_Mutation</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Nonsense_Mutation is a mutation that introduces a premature stop codon into the genetic code, truncating the protein.&lt;SEP&gt;Nonsense_Mutation is a type of genetic mutation represented in the Satpathy data set and is observed in fields such as NF1.mutation and NOTCH1.mutation.&lt;SEP&gt;Nonsense_Mutation is a type of genetic mutation that introduces a premature stop codon, leading to a truncated protein.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ef50a779ee9b01547f7b4ecb81de4aa3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0a609c332695ee10881d19b03221d781&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81847cb9abb5eeae6f99e3ef595ac88b</data>
