      <data key="d0">In_Frame_Del</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">In_Frame_Del describes an in-frame deletion mutation that removes a number of nucleotides in a gene such that the reading frame is preserved.&lt;SEP&gt;In_Frame_Del is a type of genetic mutation involving the deletion of nucleotides that does not disrupt the reading frame.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ef50a779ee9b01547f7b4ecb81de4aa3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81847cb9abb5eeae6f99e3ef595ac88b</data>
