      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Frame_Shift_Ins indicates a frameshift insertion mutation, introducing new nucleotides and altering the reading frame.&lt;SEP&gt;Frame_Shift_Ins is a type of genetic mutation involving the insertion of nucleotides that results in a shift of the reading frame.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ef50a779ee9b01547f7b4ecb81de4aa3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81847cb9abb5eeae6f99e3ef595ac88b</data>
