      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Splice_Site denotes mutations that affect the nucleotide sequence at sites where RNA splicing occurs, possibly leading to aberrant gene products.&lt;SEP&gt;Splice_Site is a type of genetic mutation present as a sample in NOTCH1.mutation in the Satpathy data set.&lt;SEP&gt;Splice_Site is a type of genetic mutation affecting the sites at which splicing of precursor mRNA takes place.</data>
