    <node id="Dou">
      <data key="d0">Dou</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Dou is a data table sourced from Source11, distinguished by its extensive coverage of fields related to proteomics, participant and patient information, and various aspects of tumor data, especially endometrial tumors. The table includes clinical, pathological, and demographic variables that detail tumor characteristics, outcomes, and participant identifiers, facilitating comprehensive clinical and pathology analyses.

Beyond its clinical focus, Dou encompasses a wide array of biological and measurement data. This includes immunological information quantified as cell proportions, as well as fields related to immune cell scoring and gene expression. Genetic and pathway activity, specifically PI3K pathway gene activity or status, are represented across multiple float64 fields, allowing for detailed analysis of pathway interactions and activities.

Dou also contains numerous genomics-related fields, such as binary indicators of gene or pathway interactions, copy number variations, and purity analysis measures for samples. The table incorporates sample information tied to sequencing, with fields related to RNAseq, miRNAseq, and methylation, offering a broad spectrum of molecular data for each case. The inclusion of records with unique and participant IDs ensures traceability and integrity across analyses.

In sum, Dou serves as an integrative dataset within Source11 that consolidates clinical, pathological, demographic, biological, immunological, genetic, and genomic data, supporting multifaceted research and analysis of endometrial and potentially other tumor types through its comprehensive field structure.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-79ff574176dbb818bd39ebca5b568487&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4ac06119fe8f3a47fa80133953298c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94eceebc5e5fb326980c5e1aff4c4a13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c082067d445456167547d0440ba3b63d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0595c3abc42031a548ce610615767cfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ee593816b40e1f778329f1904c2877d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cab940e1fe00d1b5b4f017b4600051e5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7666341cbbdce9d2b92b3cb14a67e9ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-44fbd23d798d1dc0e4bb45cbbb15a452&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-11fa8226b84559d5d3722430f779772c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d65ba32b88e919e45abe4e167e142224&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-922d8a4578a50bcf7c880dfe43b634bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4544272493731c31733ce34d1e23ba72&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2c4bb739cfbcabcd7df2d04d21fe611&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-000cebb01143a64a4e44e183c360cba3</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1772772443</data>
