    <node id="CIBERSORT_Macrophages_M2">
      <data key="d0">CIBERSORT_Macrophages_M2</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">CIBERSORT_Macrophages_M2 represents the proportion of inferred M2 macrophages in a biological sample, computed by the CIBERSORT algorithm with numeric values provided.</data>
