      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Gillette is a data table linked to Source12 that contains sample, participant, experiment, and channel fields.&lt;SEP&gt;Gillette is the name of the data table containing various participant, clinical, and experimental fields in source12.&lt;SEP&gt;Gillette is a table in the dataset from Source12 containing tumor purity, scores, QC status, and mutation fields for various genes.&lt;SEP&gt;Gillette is a table in source12 containing various genetic and clinical fields related to individuals, such as smoking history and mRNA expression.&lt;SEP&gt;Gillette is a dataset or table containing multiple fields related to genetic mutations and mutation status in various genes.&lt;SEP&gt;Gillette is the source organization or dataset table referenced as source12 for genetic and molecular data fields.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-b75a391c5f0b66b34d954f9a4cd3db18&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7c632134b01ac5b1f5e082cfa736b64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1528391f98541c081c44645142dbc460&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0c3c12a65d99f3fd6fb254162ad5f01&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2c4bb739cfbcabcd7df2d04d21fe611&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56d9b31e2fe71c27aaee333b1280d702</data>
