      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Source17 represents the dataset source for clinical and genetic data fields listed, involving cancer staging, biomarker readings, invasion indicators, genetic mutations, and patient outcomes.&lt;SEP&gt;Source17 is the original data origin referenced in the lineage of all fields and tables described.&lt;SEP&gt;Source17 is the origin for the data fields contained in the Vasaikar table and provides various genetic and clinical features.&lt;SEP&gt;Source17 is a dataset containing the Vasaikar table and associated fields related to tumor sample analysis.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-7c8a40c856b719c354d215bc913c1e47&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a16fce68df8a087312002be8f90c5ca4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbccf9869f93f2035c4a3bb576b81616&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-efe96eed9593ab805239b1a121351ac4</data>
