      <data key="d2">Huang is a data table sourced from source13 containing clinical, pathological, and molecular fields related to tumor samples.&lt;SEP&gt;Huang is the name of a dataset or table in source13 containing detailed clinical and behavioral variables.&lt;SEP&gt;Huang is the source organization or dataset table referenced as source13 for clinical and demographic fields.&lt;SEP&gt;Huang is a table or dataset sourced from source13 containing fields related to genomic classification and instability indices.</data>
