      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Channel is a field in Table Gillette referring to the channel or type of measurement used.&lt;SEP&gt;Channel is an identifier for the channel or specific measurement type, represented as a string field in the Gillette table from source12.&lt;SEP&gt;Channel is an identifier for the channel or measurement type in Satpathy sample metadata.&lt;SEP&gt;Channel is a field in the Satpathy table that identifies the channel or type of measurement performed during the experiment.</data>
