    <edge source="Source11" target="Dou">
      <data key="d7">13.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The relation (Dou, Source11) refers to the association between the data table Dou and the dataset or data source Source11. Dou is specifically identified as a table that exists within, is derived from, or is sourced directly from Source11. Source11 serves as the foundational and original provider or source for the Dou table, supplying both the data and the associated fields present within Dou.

This relationship is particularly significant in the context of proteomics and tumor-related research, where Dou is utilized as a base table for related datasets and scientific studies. Source11 is consistently recognized as the organizing and originating entity, ensuring that all structural and content-related aspects of the Dou table are rooted in its dataset. The direct sourcing of Dou from Source11 is central to both its data integrity and its relevance for ongoing research applications.</data>
